          "description": "Less than bare minimum care. When I went in for a general physical exam (first appointment with \"Dr.\" Matt Cross), I didn't realize that he and his team were not documenting a single thing I was telling them about my medical history. When I later called his office to get one of my prescriptions I mentioned refilled (in this case it was an EMERGENCY asthma inhaler that I desperately needed a refill for), I was told that there was no record of any of my medications and they were unable to assist unless I booked another appointment to be seen in person. Just for me to describe my medical history and for them to not write it down again? I will never be back, and if you're looking for a doctor that cares about his patients, you shouldn't go to this office either.",
